Interface FilterEvent

All Known Implementing Classes:
FilterEvent.FilterAddRequested, FilterEvent.FilterExecutionRequested, FilterEvent.FilterMoveRequested, FilterEvent.FilterRemoveRequested
public sealed interface FilterEvent permits FilterEvent.FilterAddRequested, FilterEvent.FilterRemoveRequested, FilterEvent.FilterMoveRequested, FilterEvent.FilterExecutionRequested
Represents a sealed interface for filter-related events in the application. Defines the possible events that can occur when managing filters, such as adding, removing, moving, or executing filters.
